♪I want to ask if you know my heart♪

4
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:19,860
=Coming For You=

5
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,780
=Episode 24=

6
00:00:30,980 --> 00:00:33,020
(Diligence and Governance)

7
00:00:34,430 --> 00:00:36,200
Your Highness,
Nai just brought a message.

8
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,470
The princess needs you.

9
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,280
I'll leave the palace now.

10
00:00:46,390 --> 00:00:47,430
You don't need to follow.

11
00:01:11,510 --> 00:01:13,200
Have you made up your mind?

12
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,640
Have you decided to enter the palace?

13
00:01:16,710 --> 00:01:17,790
I've made up my mind.

14
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:20,690
I want to tell you
some things about myself.

15
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,520
Then go ahead.

16
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:30,210
That day, you said
I was hiding things from you.

17
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,480
But what you don't know is

18
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,680
every time I wanted
to tell you the truth,

19
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:40,430
something in my mind always stopped me.

20
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,230
Maybe it was my subconscious.

21
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:46,400
I thought it was my last retreat.

22
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,120
You guessed right.

23
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:53,430
I am not the Qi Xuan
you officially married.

24
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,840
I am a different soul.

25
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,430
That painting is the key
to my coming and going.

26
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,560
You're not surprised at all.

27
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:09,280
You must've thoroughly investigated me.

28
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:10,970
No matter where you come from,

29
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:14,520
you are my officially wedded wife.

30
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,310
Su Qianyu.

31
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,590
Stop saying things so full of affection.

32
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,430
In reality,

33
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:26,190
it's all calculation.

34
00:02:26,650 --> 00:02:32,900
♪Being used to engraving your figure
as a metaphor♪

35
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,240
Forget it.

36
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,410
Let's not talk about this anymore.

37
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,150
In a few days,

38
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,120
it will be your big day.

39
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,000
I wish you

40
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,000
that all your desires come true.

41
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:55,570
♪Forgot you, fleeting, leaving no trace♪

42
00:02:56,930 --> 00:03:03,260
♪Dazed in your embrace, like a dream♪

43
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:07,380
♪A meteor crosses countless paths♪

44
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,400
I won't die, right?

45
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,280
Don't worry. I won't let you die.

46
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,430
In this body of mine,

47
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,150
you can freely do what you want.

48
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,920
I'll handle

49
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,000
everything for you.

50
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:29,190
♪Thinking of you, resenting you♪

51
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:30,870
Actually,

52
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,430
you can rely on me.

53
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,360
I...

54
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,030
Can I?

55
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:39,550
Of course.

56
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,550
I'm sorry.

57
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,920
I'm late.

58
00:03:44,690 --> 00:03:45,790
♪There's no end♪

59
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:48,860
♪Chasing your shadow♪

60
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,560
You're wrong.

61
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,630
Loving someone

62
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,960
isn't like analyzing
military intelligence.

63
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:56,990
Then what is it?

64
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,640
My wish is

65
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,810
that you'll be by my side
every year on my birthday.

66
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,630
You are my most precious gift.

67
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:15,450
♪Dazed in your embrace♪

68
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,600
Su Qianyu would never choose you.

69
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:20,480
After all, to him,

70
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,920
you are just a pawn to be used.

71
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:26,920
♪Creating ripples♪

72
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:33,780
♪I've fallen fearlessly
into the love you've woven♪

73
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:41,010
♪This is my fate intertwined with yours♪

74
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:48,380
♪Thinking of you, resenting you,
and forgetting you again♪

75
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:53,350
♪The noise fuels the madness of love♪

76
00:04:53,370 --> 00:04:54,270
Consider

77
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:55,670
this drink

78
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:58,550
as a celebration for you in advance.

79
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,310
♪There's no end♪

80
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:04,140
♪Chasing your shadow♪

81
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:11,140
♪The briefest
and most intense encounter♪

82
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:14,980
♪Holding tight to the fleeting past♪

83
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:18,840
♪Embracing you again♪

84
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:26,150
♪A tired bird loses
its forest to rest in♪

85
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:31,610
♪The flowers haven't withered;
no time for you to see me off♪

86
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:34,910
This time,
it's finally my turn to outsmart you.

87
00:05:34,910 --> 00:05:41,890
♪Let me think of you alone
when all falls silent♪

88
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,200
Qi Xuan.

89
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,560
Why?

90
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,170
Why are you doing this to me?

91
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:59,600
Why leave me alone, Qi Xuan?

92
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,310
Qi Xuan, why?

93
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,310
Forgive me.

94
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,720
The road back

95
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,190
is not just the painting.

96
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,120
I've already regretted it.

97
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,200
I don't want anything else.

98
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,480
As long as you stay here...

99
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,480
As long as you live well,

100
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,680
I don't care about anything else.

101
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,200
It's too late.

102
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,040
Forget me.

103
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,600
Just pretend we never met.

104
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:43,900
♪Thinking of you, resenting you♪

105
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:47,890
♪And forgetting you again♪

106
00:06:47,890 --> 00:06:54,880
♪The noise fuels the madness of love♪

107
00:06:55,360 --> 00:07:00,380
♪Holding you tight empties me;
there's no end♪

108
00:07:00,380 --> 00:07:03,480
♪Chasing your shadow♪

109
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:10,680
Long live the emperor.

110
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:17,270
♪Holding tight to the fleeting past;
embracing you again♪

111
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:18,610
(Seems it's always been this way.)

112
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,110
(The things I care about)

113
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,070
(always can't stay by my side.)

114
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,320
♪The flowers haven't withered♪

115
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,320
Why give me this?

116
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,310
Because the rabbit
is very important to you.

117
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,400
Don't worry.

118
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:36,510
I will always be by your side.

119
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,830
I made this especially for you.

120
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:47,560
It symbolizes the bond
between husband and wife.

121
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,630
You can't take it off.

122
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,400
Do you understand?

123
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:58,600
(You said you'd always be by my side.)

124
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,600
(It's all a lie.)

125
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:23,630
(This is...)

126
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,440
Su Qianyu, you've finally woken up.

127
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,440
Where am I?

128
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:49,270
You got into a car accident
while saving a girl.

129
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,110
You've been unconscious until now.

130
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:06,870
Qi Xuan.

131
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:12,390
(Could it all have been a dream?)

132
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,270
Forget me.

133
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:17,910
Just pretend we never met.

134
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,500
(At first, I didn't understand
the meaning of the painting.)

135
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,540
(Now, I realize
I am the one in the painting.)

136
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:39,750
(Time that has passed)

137
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,630
(can never be retained.)

138
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,270
(I will never make you smile again.)

139
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,390
(Maybe...)

140
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:06,980
(Divorce Agreement)

141
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:20,760
♪That day, your light illuminated me♪

142
00:10:21,380 --> 00:10:26,440
♪I saw that holding on
would eventually bring a response♪

143
00:10:27,090 --> 00:10:32,580
♪Unafraid of the fierce storms
and the long journey ahead♪

144
00:10:33,410 --> 00:10:34,320
(Maybe)

145
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,400
(it's farewell)

146
00:10:37,130 --> 00:10:38,450
(and a chance to see you again.)

147
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:42,840
♪That day, your light illuminated me♪

148
00:10:56,930 --> 00:10:59,670
♪Gazing at distant mountains far away♪

149
00:11:00,110 --> 00:11:02,960
♪Waiting for the peach blossoms
to bloom on the branches♪

150
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:07,900
♪With petals falling on the balcony,
you step into the morning glow♪

151
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:12,670
♪Painting a scroll
of splendid mountains and seas♪

152
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,880
♪In the depths of the clouds,
leaving space for you♪

153
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:21,610
♪Wandering together,
no need to wait any longer♪

154
00:11:22,310 --> 00:11:25,520
♪Green grasses grow; willows sway♪

155
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:28,770
♪Ripples spread before my eyes♪

156
00:11:28,770 --> 00:11:34,770
♪I want to ask if you know my heart♪

157
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:41,820
♪The spring breeze
stirs my thoughts in the painting♪

158
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:45,080
♪The summer rain
sends my letters in dreams♪

159
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:47,050
♪Whether the ink is dark or light♪

160
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:50,650
♪The sea and the fields change;
I wish to see you again♪

161
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:54,470
♪The autumn moon hides deep in poems,
holding affection♪

162
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:58,110
♪The winter snow sighs
for the passing years♪

163
00:11:58,430 --> 00:12:03,710
♪I only wish
to watch the world with you♪

